.hk/egazette/pdf/20202444e/cs220202444136.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gld.gov.hk%2Fegazette%2Fpdf%2F20202444e%2Fcs220202444136.pdf&d=6wD9ZzBID4i2v0E%2BCeDzwPUUj30esm9w7dCaRgXMgeE%3D&h=4df2cc40\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.gld.gov.hk/egazette/pdf/20202444e/cs220202444136.pdf</a></strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"b6ce03a6d91c22be5d1b64ede289683627a55cea","tid":2087663,"uid":19817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T01:54:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2086300/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2086300/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>係時候到我地守護番正義女神</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我想破2千正評, 留個紀念得唔得, 推番行動POST優先"}]}